      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i think i get the temp part. but can u be more specific about the chemistry? like, what exactly are the amino acids and sugars doing to each other at a molecular level to cause that color change? i need the actual scientific details for my exam.",
      "source": "evaluator"
